 .../bindings/thermal/mediatek,thermal.yaml                  |  2 ++
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt6797.dtsi                    | 19 +++++++++-
 drivers/iio/adc/mt6577_auxadc.c                             |  1 +
